subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution and habitat: —This Amazonian species is found in Brazil , Colombia , Ecuador and Peru ( Judziewicz & Clark 1993 ,
Vorontsova et al. 2016
). In Brazil , it is registered in Amazonas state ( Viana 2020 ) and this is the first record for Pará state. This species occurs in wet lowland forests at elevations from 30 to 300 meters ( Judziewicz & Clark 1993 ). In the Serra do Cachimbo, it was found in Open ombrophilous forest, along the Curuá rivers margins.
